kea.schedule.scheduleservice.controllers

Class CRUDAbstractController<E extends ModelInterface,S extends CRUDServiceInterface<E>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • kea.schedule.scheduleservice.controllers.CRUDAbstractController<E,S>
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CRUDCourseController, CRUDLectureController, CRUDLectureItemController, CRUDLectureSubjectController, CRUDSubjectPriorityController

    public abstract class CRUDAbstractController<E extends ModelInterface,S extends CRUDServiceInterface<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract implementation of a CRUD controller. This abstract implementation expect a POJO object to be created. The POJO object must implement ModelInterface The POJO can get simple datatypes set from the MSCRUDAbstractController.
